>function great operated from the interior, so something is wrong w/ the 
>mechanism in the door, I'm guessing. My machanic replaced a spring that he 
>said was problematic and it worked great for 10 minutes! Any wisdom from 
>experienced lock surgeons? Thanks, Craig

